# Project Conventions (Maverick)

## Authority

**Highest authority.** Overrides generic AI preferences and framework boilerplate. When in doubt, match existing code.

## Package & Brand

- Package: `maverick-website` v1.0.0
- Brand: **Mavverik** | Contact: `contact@mavverik.com`
- Tagline: *"Production AI the regulators sign off on."*

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|------------|---------|
| Framework | Next.js App Router | 15.5.19 |
| UI | React | 19.2.7 |
| Language | TypeScript (strict) | 5.9.3 |
| Styling | Tailwind + Signal Slate CSS vars | 3.4.19 |
| Animation | Framer Motion | 11.18.2 |
| Deploy | Vercel + semver tags | `docs/VERSIONING.md` |

**Not in use:** API routes, global state, test runner (yet), ESLint/Prettier, CI config in repo.

## Folder Structure

```
maverick/
├── app/components/     # Reusable UI + index.ts
├── app/sections/       # Page sections + index.ts
├── app/hooks/          # Custom hooks
├── app/globals.css     # Design tokens + component classes
├── app/layout.tsx      # Root layout
├── app/page.tsx        # Server page composition
├── lib/utils.ts        # cn(), tokens, contact constants
├── public/             # Static assets
├── docs/VERSIONING.md  # Release workflow
├── design-reviews/     # Design notes (not runtime)
├── AGENTS.md           # Agent handbook
└── .cursor/rules/      # AI engineering OS
```

## Page Composition

```
Navigation → main#main-content → [Hero, Founders, Services, Contact] → Footer
```

## Section Contract

| Section | id | Nav hash | File |
|---------|-----|----------|------|
| Hero | `hero` | `#hero` | `app/sections/Hero.tsx` |
| Founders | `founders` | `#founders` | `app/sections/Founders.tsx` |
| Services | `services` | `#services` | `app/sections/Services.tsx` |
| Contact | `contact` | `#contact` | `app/sections/Contact.tsx` |

## Naming

| Type | Pattern |
|------|---------|
| Components/Sections | PascalCase `.tsx`, named export |
| Hooks | camelCase `use*` |
| Props | `ComponentNameProps` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE |
| Section IDs | lowercase kebab |

## Import Order

`"use client"` → React → third-party → `@/lib/utils` → relative → local data

## Architecture

- **State:** Local `useState`/`useEffect` only
- **Contact:** `CONTACT_EMAIL`, `CONTACT_MAILTO`, `BRIEF_MAILTO` in `lib/utils.ts`
- **Nav:** Hash scroll via `scrollIntoView`; nav theme tracks `#hero` (dark overlay)
- **Animations:** Framer `useInView`; see `10-technology-rules.mdc`

## Shared Utilities (`lib/utils.ts`)

`cn()`, `space`, `layout`, `type`, `container`, `section`, `surface`, `anchor`, contact constants, `getContactIntentLabel()`

## Components

| Component | Role |
|-----------|------|
| `Navigation.tsx` | Fixed nav, mobile drawer, scroll theme |
| `Footer.tsx` | Site footer |
| `HeroVideoBackground.tsx` | Hero video + reduced-motion fallback |
| `SignalGraph.tsx` | SVG wave fallback |
| `Seal.tsx` | Governance seal mark |

## Build & Validation

```bash
npm run dev      # Local development
npm run build    # Required gate
npm run start    # Production serve
npx tsc --noEmit # TypeScript check
```

No CI/CD in repo. When tests/CI are added, update `02-validation-loops.mdc` and `99-completion-gate.mdc`.

## Existing Workflows (Preserve)

| Workflow | Doc |
|----------|-----|
| Agentic development | `AGENTS.md`, `.cursor/rules/` |
| Versioning & deploy | `docs/VERSIONING.md` |
| Design reviews | `design-reviews/` |

## Out of Scope (Unless Requested)

API routes, backend, global state, unrelated refactors, committing MCP/editor configs.

## Self-Improvement

When architecture changes: update this file, `10-technology-rules.mdc`, and `PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md`.
